    <div class="story-card__description">
                
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/michigan-bottled-water-whitmer-flint">
                                    Michigan Bottlers Still Get Free Water, Despite Whitmer’s Tough Talk
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            Gov. Gretchen Whitmer had pledged to crack down on bottled water companies taking water at the same time Flint, Michigan, faced a water crisis. Six years later and in her second term, little has changed.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/anna-clark">Anna Clark</a>, photography by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/sarahbeth-maney">Sarahbeth Maney</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2024-06-06EDT05:00">June 6, 5 a.m. EDT</time>
        </p>

